    {
      "name": "root_cause",
      "displayName": "Root Cause — Data Quality Defects",
      "layout": [
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "header",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "## Root Cause — 8 Data Quality Defects Across 6 Dimensions\n",
                "\n",
                "Each KPI divergence traces to a specific data quality defect. The **same underlying tables** are queried by both reports — the difference is how each team handles ambiguous or defective data."
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 0,
            "y": 0,
            "width": 12,
            "height": 2
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "defect_table",
            "queries": [
              {
                "name": "main_query",
                "query": {
                  "datasetName": "report_divergence",
                  "fields": [
                    {
                      "name": "root_cause",
                      "expression": "`root_cause`"
                    },
                    {
                      "name": "kpi",
                      "expression": "`kpi`"
                    },
                    {
                      "name": "divergence",
                      "expression": "`divergence`"
                    },
                    {
                      "name": "explanation",
                      "expression": "`explanation`"
                    }
                  ],
                  "disaggregated": true
                }
              }
            ],
            "spec": {
              "version": 2,
              "frame": {
                "title": "Defect Impact Summary",
                "showTitle": true
              },
              "widgetType": "table",
              "encodings": {
                "columns": [
                  {
                    "fieldName": "root_cause",
                    "displayName": "DQ Dimension"
                  },
                  {
                    "fieldName": "kpi",
                    "displayName": "Affected KPI"
                  },
                  {
                    "fieldName": "divergence",
                    "format": {
                      "type": "number-plain",
                      "abbreviation": "none",
                      "decimalPlaces": {
                        "type": "exact",
                        "places": 1
                      }
                    },
                    "displayName": "Gap"
                  },
                  {
                    "fieldName": "explanation",
                    "displayName": "How the Defect Causes Divergence"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 6,
            "y": 2,
            "width": 6,
            "height": 5
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "completeness_detail",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### COMPLETENESS\n",
                "**Defect**: NULL `allowed_amount` on 8% of paid claims (concentrated on high-charge MRI/NM/IR modalities)\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report A**: Excludes NULL rows from net collections denominator\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report B**: Substitutes `charge_amount` ($2,800–$8,500) into denominator, dramatically inflating it\n",
                "\n",
                "**Result**: Net Collection Rate diverges **6.5 percentage points**"
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 0,
            "y": 7,
            "width": 4,
            "height": 4
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "validity_detail",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### VALIDITY\n",
                "**Defect**: 30% of denied claims have invalid CARC codes (CO-999, PI-300, OA-500) that don't exist in X12 835 standard\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report A**: Drops invalid CARC codes — since those claims ONLY have invalid denials, they're removed entirely from the denied count\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report B**: Counts ALL denials regardless of CARC validity\n",
                "\n",
                "**Result**: Denial Rate diverges **3.9 percentage points**"
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 4,
            "y": 7,
            "width": 4,
            "height": 4
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "timeliness_detail",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### TIMELINESS\n",
                "**Defect**: Hospital-based locations (system_a) have AR snapshots 9 days stale (last: May 6 vs today: May 15)\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report A**: Uses MAX(snapshot_date) per location — includes hospitals' low-AR data (avg 22 days)\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report B**: Filters to snapshot_date = TODAY only — excludes hospitals entirely, leaving freestanding (avg 60 days)\n",
                "\n",
                "**Result**: Days in AR diverges **13 days**"
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 8,
            "y": 7,
            "width": 4,
            "height": 4
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "consistency_detail",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### CONSISTENCY\n",
                "**Defect**: `claim_header.payer_name` uses 3–5 name variants per payer (e.g., \"BCBS\", \"Blue Cross BS\", \"BCBS IL\", \"BlueCross BlueShield of IL\")\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report A**: JOINs to canonical `payer` reference table on `payer_id` — correct classification\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report B**: Pattern-matches on `payer_name` with incomplete lookup — misses variants like \"UHC\", \"CVS/Aetna\"\n",
                "\n",
                "**Result**: Commercial Mix diverges **19.5 percentage points**"
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 0,
            "y": 11,
            "width": 4,
            "height": 4
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "uniqueness_detail",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### UNIQUENESS + ACCURACY-A\n",
                "**Defect 1**: 3% of pre-Oct 2025 claims are unflagged rebill duplicates (`is_rebill=false`, `original_claim_id=NULL`)\n",
                "\n",
                "**Defect 2**: 1.5% of claims have TC/26 component overlap (global + technical + professional lines for same CPT)\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report A**: Deduplicates by (encounter, patient, charge); removes components when global exists\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report B**: Sums all claim lines naively\n",
                "\n",
                "**Result**: Total Charges diverges **$4.5M**"
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 4,
            "y": 11,
            "width": 4,
            "height": 4
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "accuracy_detail",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### ACCURACY (B + C)\n",
                "**Defect B**: PAY-011/PAY-012 clearinghouse error sets `allowed_amount = charge_amount` (should be 40–60% of charge)\n",
                "\n",
                "**Defect C**: BCBS (PAY-001) Jan–Feb 2026 uses stale fee schedule — `allowed_amount` 12% below actual payment\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report A**: Reconciles against `payment` table; uses actual payments for affected payers\n",
                "\n",
                "**Report B**: Trusts `allowed_amount` at face value\n",
                "\n",
                "**Result**: Net Revenue diverges **$4.1M**"
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 8,
            "y": 11,
            "width": 4,
            "height": 4
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "divergence_bar",
            "queries": [
              {
                "name": "main_query",
